data.title: Utah Jazz vs. Chicago Bulls: Opponent Game Thread Highlights
data.meta_description: FYI I’ve been told the second half of the game thread often doesn’t show up when viewing these posts in the Twitter app’s reader mode. Today's Opponent Game Thread host: Blog A Bull. Bulls give up one of the most points ever in a non OT game And what do they do? They promptly give…
data.text:
Bulls give up one of the most points ever in a non OT game

And what do they do? They promptly give the fucking bumbling clusterfuck of a coach a pay raise. Hey you really fucking completely fucking blow at your job and are a completely inept jackass so here’s a pay raise!! Are the Bulls even a real team or is this just a really spooky mind bending episode of Black Mirror?

Posted by Mitch Slapped on Jan 12, 2019 | 6:48 PM

This is just insane

Fuck this team!

Posted by shiu413 on Jan 12, 2019 | 8:30 PM
